{"blogid": "126672178", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "253", "writerCollect": "787", "writerComment": "166", "writerFan": "2204", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "3586", "writerName": "老师好我是大白", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_126672178.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "5024", "writerRankWeekly": "2190", "writerThumb": "414", "writerVisitNum": "162381", "blog_read_count": "872", "blog_time": "于 2022-09-03 00:02:26 发布", "blog_title": "华为欧拉系统安装", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h3><a id=\"_0\"></a>简介</h3>\n<p><strong>openEuler 是由开放原子开源基金会（OpenAtom Foundation）孵化及运营的开源项目</strong></p>\n<p>openEuler是一款开源操作系统。当前openEuler内核源于Linux，支持鲲鹏及其它多种处理器，能够充分释放计算芯片的潜能，是由全球开源贡献者构建的高效、稳定、安全的开源操作系统，适用于数据库、大数据、云计算、人工智能等应用场景。同时，openEuler是一个面向全球的操作系统开源社区，通过社区合作，打造创新平台，构建支持多处理器架构、统一和开放的操作系统，推动软硬件应用生态繁荣发展。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\553238dcab3e42189ba1d103ac0b71f5.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_7\"></a>最小硬件要求</h3>\n<p>安装 openEuler 22.03-LTS 所需的最小硬件要求</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>部件名称</th><th>最小硬件要求</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>CPU</td><td>鲲鹏 920（架构为AArch64）x86-64（Skylake以上）</td></tr><tr><td>内存</td><td>不小于8GB</td></tr><tr><td>硬盘</td><td>不小于120GB</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><a id=\"_16\"></a>开始安装</h2>\n<h3><a id=\"_18\"></a>选择操作系统的语言</h3>\n<p>一般选择英文（English）;如果需要安装可视化的界面；可以选择简体中文。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\57c400c841e04f5783d539bd4d448e3e.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_22\"></a>磁盘分区</h3>\n<p>默认分区即可<br/> 例如默认100G硬盘；/目录下会有60G, /home目录下会有39G的样子</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\3a49113dce59457d87f977a6c51c0e3f.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_28\"></a>软件选择</h3>\n<p>选择 Server (服务器)<br/> Server (服务器) 有一些常用的Linux命令，比如，<code>tar、ifconfig、netstat等命令。</code></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\3f744f09012543e7b5f80fce6fb8eb97.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_35\"></a>开启网卡</h3>\n<p>笔记本上的虚拟机我一般使用NAT的网络模式，比较简单快捷，也可以和笔记本直接连接。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\469bd939f7b24da49f6f72d17439837d.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_41\"></a>设置账号密码</h3>\n<p>设置root用户的账号密码<br/> ● 欧拉系统的账号密码要求比较严格，需要设置密码复杂度</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\8274a1cb6bde471b966cddf556d11f61.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_47\"></a>开始安装系统</h3>\n<p>设置完成后，就可以安装系统啦，这时候需要等待30分钟到60分钟，你可以用这个空闲时间，喝一杯卡布奇诺。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\14804990c46541d7bed9e88ed30f0efd.png\"/><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\8da3be5c4bfe4fe6b887a09c8307eed4.png\"/></p>\n<h3><a id=\"_53\"></a>重启</h3>\n<p>安装完成，重启即可。<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\ec876f06c2834ca78238c9d431593810.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\f6fb17b9f71249538233e9b838ed20a6.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"_59\"></a>查看网卡信息</h2>\n<p>网卡的配文件路径一般为: /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ 目录下ifcfg开头的的文件</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens34\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">TYPE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>Ethernet    \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">PROXY_METHOD</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>none   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">BROWSER_ONLY</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>no     \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">BOOTPROTO</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>static  \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">DEFROUTE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>yes       \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>no   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6INIT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>yes         \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6_AUTOCONF</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>yes   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6_DEFROUTE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>yes   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>no    \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6_ADDR_GEN_MODE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>stable-privacy   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NAME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ens34    \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">UUID</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>8c75c2ba-d363-46d7-9a17-6719934267b7  \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">DEVICE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ens34   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">ONBOOT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>yes \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPADDR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.103.203   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NETMASK</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">255.255</span>.255.0   \n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">GATEWAY</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.103.1   \n</code></pre>\n<h2><a id=\"_87\"></a>重启网卡</h2>\n<p>openEuler系统需要通过reboot命令重启网卡；重启后，可以看到修改好的的IP地址</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">reboot</span>\n</code></pre>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}